583
00:39:35,380 --> 00:39:37,290
I see all of it.

584
00:39:40,290 --> 00:39:42,790
That’s just how Ma is — loyal to the core

585
00:39:42,790 --> 00:39:45,580
You show him heart, he shows you loyalty.

586
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:49,960
Thank you, Ma

587
00:39:49,960 --> 00:39:51,130
Thank you, Tony

588
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,330
By the way,

589
00:39:57,330 --> 00:39:59,210
I actually came to give you an update

590
00:39:59,210 --> 00:40:00,420
back in the dorm

591
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:02,170
Lee Xun and Yuchuan were talking about

592
00:40:02,170 --> 00:40:04,080
the client who saved Chang Yihao today.

593
00:40:04,080 --> 00:40:05,460
They already figured out

594
00:40:05,460 --> 00:40:08,170
it was Lee Xiaozhen — the lawyer of Azure Dragon Syndicate

595
00:40:13,460 --> 00:40:15,170
Do they have a plan?

596
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:16,710
Not yet

597
00:40:17,670 --> 00:40:19,460
But they also mentioned

598
00:40:19,460 --> 00:40:21,170
they know Azure Dragon Syndicate's rule:

599
00:40:21,170 --> 00:40:24,040
no hurting the elderly, women or children.

600
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:26,670
Lee Xun’s been digging into it, too.

601
00:40:27,330 --> 00:40:28,960
They really want to know

602
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,040
why the gang

603
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:31,540
has never dared mess with the club.

604
00:40:33,420 --> 00:40:34,670
Got it

605
00:40:36,290 --> 00:40:37,460
I'll head out then

606
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:39,710
Thanks, Ma

607
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:40,830
Thanks, Tony

608
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,290
Look like...

609
00:40:49,290 --> 00:40:50,580
Lee Xun’s going to uncover your secrets

610
00:40:50,580 --> 00:40:52,080
sooner than later

611
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:59,170
While Hsu Chenghan’s away,

612
00:40:59,170 --> 00:41:01,960
I’ll need you to keep an eye on Yuchuan.

613
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,630
Bro.

614
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:06,790
do we really need to be this formal?

615
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:10,040
Don’t forget, I was the one looking after Yuchuan

616
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:11,750
before Hsu Chenghan came along

617
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,880
It's so pretty

618
00:41:49,170 --> 00:41:52,250
I’ve imagined this moment a thousand times.

619
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:54,750
Standing here

620
00:41:55,330 --> 00:41:57,000
looking out at the skyline…

621
00:41:59,790 --> 00:42:01,040
with you by my side.

622
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:05,750
This exact scene

623
00:42:05,750 --> 00:42:08,290
has appeared in my mind countless times

624
00:42:20,250 --> 00:42:21,630
Pan Hao

625
00:42:24,420 --> 00:42:26,250
We...

626
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,880
Let's be together

